settings.title: How it works
settings.content:
Incorporating the right nutrients into your daily routine can be an essential step toward achieving whole body health and circadian rythm support for your short and long term goals. Our Stress Support Gummies make it easy to take care of yourself without any added stress.

We recommend taking one gummy daily, either at or around the time of a meal or snack, to ensure optimal absorption. By taking the gummies with some food containing fat, your body can naturally support the absorption of essential fat-soluble vitamins in our product, allowing you to enjoy maximum benefits, however it is not mandatory.

To ensure safety and efficacy, follow the recommended dosage and only exceed it if your healthcare practitioner advises. Remember, taking too much can lead to potential toxicity and adverse effects.

When it comes to the safety of our loved ones, it's vital to keep our Stress Support Gummies out of reach of children. Our product is safe for adults, but children's bodies may not be able to handle the vitamins' dosage effectively, so it's best to be cautious.

Finally, keeping our gummies in a cool, dry place without direct sunlight can help maintain their efficacy and quality. You shouldn't have to worry about stress when you're taking care of yourself; with our Stress Support Gummies, you won't have to.

Vitamin B12, or cobalamin, is naturally found in animal foods. It can also be added to foods or supplements.
Vitamin A, also known as retinol, has several important functions.
Vitamin D3 is best known for strengthening your bones, which it does by helping the body absorb calcium and phosphorus from food
Phytonadione (vitamin K1) is a medication used to treat and manage vitamin K deficiency, which is a significant risk factor for intracranial hemorrhage and other bleeds
It contributes to skin health and bone metabolism, promotes proper brain function and prevents heart-related diseases.

settings.question: How does targeting Whole Body Health & Circadian Rhythm support my overall well-being & healthy aging?
settings.answer:
In our fast-paced world, factors like stress, traveling, environmental changes, and unhealthy diets can impact our overall well-being and how we age. 

Embracing whole body health and aligning with our natural circadian rhythms is crucial for a vibrant and balanced life.
Imagine your body as a thriving, interconnected ecosystem made up of trillions of enzymes, microorganisms, and fungi. 

Nourishing this complex network with essential nutrients, beneficial bacteria, digestive enzymes, and natural adaptogens promotes comprehensive health and well-being from within.

By aligning your body's internal ecosystem with your circadian rhythms, you promote holistic wellness that lays the foundation for a strong, resilient, and balanced life.

settings.question: Why Are Probiotics Important?
settings.answer:
Probiotics are live microorganisms known that are ingested through supplements or fermented meals.

More and more research indicates a connection between general health and disease and the balance or imbalance of bacteria in your digestive system.

Probiotics have been linked to a variety of health advantages and help maintain a healthy balance of gut bacteria.

A few of the advantages include that they promote weight loss, help maintain digestive and immunological health, and more.

We love using probiotics in our gummy vitamins because they can help prevent gastrointestinal disorders and strengthen one's immune system.

settings.question: What are terpenes, and how do they enhance vitamin gummies?
settings.answer: Terpenes are aromatic compounds found in plants that can have various health benefits. When added to vitamin gummies, terpenes can enhance their flavor, aroma, and potential health benefits.

settings.question: Are Probiotic Gummies Effective?
settings.answer: While probiotic gummies are as effective as other supplements that contain probiotics, gummies do not always contain the same amount of live cultures. Therefore, not all gummies will have the same impact or provide the same digestive advantage.

settings.question: What Are Digestive Enzymes?
settings.answer:
The food you eat needs to be broken down by digestive enzymes. These proteins accelerate the chemical processes that transform food into compounds that can be absorbed by your digestive system.

There are digesting enzymes in your saliva. They are also expelled by a few of your organs, such as the gallbladder, liver, and pancreas. Digestive enzymes are also kept in cells that line the outside of your intestines.

However, you can also add digestive enzymes into your diet if you need to improve your body's performance, digestion, and recovery. All our ActiveCare products follow a multi-enzyme approach that ensures superior absorption of vital macro and micro nutrients in your body and throughout your daily diet.

settings.question: Are Gummy Vitamins Beneficial?
settings.answer:
Yes, there are numerous benefits to gummy vitamins. The following people will benefit the most from taking gummy vitamins:

People who forget to take vitamins:
Taking vitamins doesn't have to feel like a chore anymore! Our gummy dietary supplement is a great way to make health fun, flavorful, and interesting.

Those who can't swallow pills:
Gummy vitamins are an excellent way to get your nutrients in if you struggle to swallow pills.

Those with dietary restrictions:
If you have certain food allergies, gummies can help you get the nutrients you might be lacking from not being able to eat those foods; for example, if you can’t drink milk, our adults’ gummy calcium dietary supplement will be a great substitute. 

Fortunately, ActiveCare has the best multi-nutrient gummy to support your whole body health and aging.
